[This press report indicates that there may be as many as 20 cases of
mumps among students at the UC Berkeley campus.

Berkeley is situated on the east shore of San Francisco Bay in
Northern California. It can be located in the HealthMap/ProMED-mail
interactive map at http://healthmap.org/r/1jDz. - Mod.CP]
